## §4. Phase α–ε — hxq-molglue-ar-001 candidate

- **Phase α (target select)**: AR-V7 splice variant (castration-resistant prostate cancer; ARV-110 misses AR-V7 ligand-binding domain). Target = full-length AR + AR-V7 NTD-binder.
- **Phase β (E3 select)**: atypical E3 — DCAF16 (covalent recruit) or KEAP1 (Nrf2 paradigm reverse) — beyond CRBN/VHL.
- **Phase γ (linker design)**: rigid spiro-piperidine 8–12 atom linker; W-axis combinatorial library 96-member.
- **Phase δ (Q-validation)**: VQE ternary complex energy < −12 kcal/mol; cooperativity α > 5.
- **Phase ε (clinical hand-off)**: hxq-molglue-ar-001 → AR/AR-V7 dual degrader, mCRPC post-ARV-110, post-enzalutamide setting.

## §5. raw#10 honest C3 — induced proximity paradigm

induced proximity 의 historical arc 는 1957 thalidomide tragedy 로 시작 (phocomelia birth defect, ~10,000 affected; teratogen 으로 withdrawn). 1998 multiple myeloma re-purpose 로 부활 (Singhal et al, NEJM 1999); 2010 Ito et al (Science) "thalidomide binds CRBN" 발견 → 2014 Lu/Krönke "lenalidomide degrades IKZF1/3 via CRBN" → CRBN molecular glue paradigm 확립. 2010s 후반 PROTAC explosion (Crews lab founding Arvinas 2013, Kymera 2018, C4 Therapeutics 2016). 2026 현재 ARV-471 vepdegestrant Phase 3 ER+/HER2- breast cancer (post-CDK4/6) 진행, KT-474 Phase 2 atopic dermatitis (Sanofi $1.5B deal) 진행, mezigdomide/golcadomide Phase 3 hematologic 진행. LYTAC (Bertozzi 2020 Nature) extracellular protein paradigm, AUTAC (Arimoto 2019), RIBOTAC (Disney 2018) 으로 induced proximity 가 cytosolic UPS 너머 lysosome / autophagy / RNA 로 확장. 양자 fit: ternary complex geometry 가 cooperativity α 를 결정하고 (α>>1 induced fit, α=1 equilibrium, α<1 negative cooperativity), 이는 quantum chemistry 정밀 계산 영역. 한국 K-pharma PROTAC 진입 — 한미약품 PROTAC platform, 유한양행 partnership, Daewoong Therapeutics PROTAC pipeline. drug-like properties challenges: hookeffect (high-dose 에서 binary complex 만 형성되어 ternary 감소), oral bioavailability (분자량 800-1200Da Lipinski 위배), permeability, metabolic stability — 이를 nano-delivery (NB-axis) 로 rescue. future direction: covalent-PROTAC (DCAF16 covalent, KEAP1 covalent) — platform_covalent overlap; CRBN-independent E3 expansion (DCAF15 indisulam, DCAF16, FEM1B, RNF114); dual-E3 PROTAC; antibody-PROTAC conjugate (AbTAC); brain-penetrant PROTAC (CNS PROTAC for neurodegeneration).

